 (rank)|Private]]), and Rittmester ([[Rittmeister]]) instead of Kaptein ([[Captain (land)|Captain]]).\n\n\nThe ranks of ''Grenader'' and ''Matros'' were bestowed upon soldiers who have finished the 12 months compulsory service and had signed one or more three-year contracts to continue serving. The ranks of ''Visekorporal/Visekonstabel/Vingsoldat'' ([[Corporal]]/Leading Rate) were usually ascribed to soldiers with long and/or outstanding service, though may be bestowed on soldiers with extra responsibilities (e.g. the shift-commander among a group of soldiers on guard-duty). A ''UB-Korporal/Kvartermesteraspirant'' (Rate Corporal/Petty Officer-in-training) was a soldier who has finished the UB course ''(Utskrevet Befalskurs)'', a course intended to prepare conscripted soldiers for non-commissioned officer duties, but still under training in \"the field\". After one-year course and service these soldiers were qualified for the rank of ''Sersjant'' or ''Kvartermester''.\n\n====Officers====\n{| style=\"border:1px solid #8888aa; background-color:#f7f8ff; padding:5px; font-size:95%; margin: 0px 12px 12px 0px;\"\n{{Ranks and Insignia of NATO Armed Forces/OF/Blank}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n! rowspan=2| {{flagicon|Norway}} Army &<br />Air force\n| colspan=2 rowspan=2| '''''No equivalent'''''\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF9.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF8.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF7.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF6.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF5.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF4.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF3.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_OF2.png|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:NOR_OF1.png|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:FenrikOF1.png|50px]]\n| colspan=12 rowspan=2| '''''No equivalent'''''\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| colspan=2| General\n| colspan=2| Generall\u00f8ytnant\n| colspan=2| Generalmajor\n| colspan=2| Brigader\n| colspan=2| Oberst\n| colspan=2| Oberstl\u00f8ytnant\n| colspan=2| Major\n| colspan=2| Kaptein/<br>Rittmester\n| colspan=3| L\u00f8ytnant\n| colspan=3| Fenrik\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n! rowspan=2| {{flagicon|Norway|naval}} Navy\n| colspan=2 rowspan=2| '''''No equivalent'''''\n| colspan=2| [[File:Of9 sj\u00f8.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Of8 sj\u00f8.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Of7 sj\u00f8.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Of6 sj\u00f8.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Generic-Navy-O7.svg|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Generic-Navy-O6.svg|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Generic-Navy-O5.svg|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Generic-Navy-O4.svg|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:Generic-Navy-O3.svg|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:Generic-Navy-O1.svg|50px]]\n| colspan=12 rowspan=2| '''''No equivalent'''''\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| colspan=2| Admiral\n| colspan=2| Viseadmiral\n| colspan=2| Kontreadmiral\n| colspan=2| Flaggkommand\u00f8r\n| colspan=2| Kommand\u00f8r\n| colspan=2| Kommand\u00f8rkaptein \n| colspan=2| Orlogskaptein\n| colspan=2| Kapteinl\u00f8ytnant\n| colspan=3| L\u00f8ytnant\n| colspan=3| Fenrik\n|}\n\n====Enlisted====\nThe rank insignia for enlisted for the army, navy and air force respectively.\n{| style=\"border:1px solid #8888aa; background-color:#f7f8ff; padding:5px; font-size:95%; margin: 0px 12px 12px 0px;\"\n{{Ranks and Insignia of NATO Armies/OR/Blank}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| rowspan=3| '''{{flagicon|Norway}} [[Norwegian Army|Norway]]'''\n| colspan=16 rowspan=3| '''''No equivalent'''''{{hr}}\n| colspan=6| [[File:OR5.png|50px]]\n| colspan=4| [[File:GrenOR4.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[FILE:OR3.png|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:Gren OR2.png|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:Visekorporal OR2.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:Menig OR1.png|50px]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| colspan=6| Sersjant\n| colspan=4| Korporal\n| colspan=2| Visekorporal 1. klasse\n| colspan=6| Visekorporal\n| colspan=2| Menig\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| colspan=6| [[Sergeant]]\n| colspan=4| [[Corporal]]\n| colspan=2| [[Lance Corporal|Master Lance Corporal]]\n| colspan=6| [[Lance Corporal]]\n| colspan=2| [[Private (rank)|Private]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| rowspan=3| '''{{flagicon|Norway|naval}} [[Norwegian Navy|Norway]]'''\n| colspan=16 rowspan=3| '''''No equivalent'''''{{hr}}\n| colspan=6| [[File:NOR_NavyOR5.png|50px]]\n| colspan=4| [[File:NOR_NavyOR4.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2 rowspan=3| '''''No equivalent'''''\n| colspan=6| [[File:NOR_NavyOR2.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:NOR_NavyOR1.png|50px]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| colspan=6| Kvartermester\n| colspan=4| Konstabel\n| colspan=6| Visekonstabel\n| colspan=2| Menig\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| colspan=6| [[Sergeant]]\n| colspan=4| [[Corporal]]\n| colspan=6| [[Seaman (rank)|Seaman]]\n| colspan=2| [[Seaman recruit|Junior Seaman]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| rowspan=3| '''{{flagicon|Norway}} [[Norwegian Army|Norway]]'''\n| colspan=16 rowspan=3| '''''No equivalent'''''{{hr}}\n| colspan=6| [[File:FlyOR5.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:GrenKorp.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:FlyOR4.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[FILE:GrenVingsoldat1.png|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:GrenVingsoldat.png|50px]]\n| colspan=3| [[File:FlyOR2.png|50px]]\n| colspan=2| [[File:FlyOR1.png|50px]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| colspan=6| Sersjant\n| colspan=4| Korporal\n| colspan=2| Visekorporal 1. klasse\n| colspan=6| Visekorporal\n| colspan=2| Flysoldat\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n| colspan=6| [[Sergeant]]\n| colspan=4| [[Corporal]]\n| colspan=2| [[Lance Corporal|Master Lance Corporal]]\n| colspan=6| [[Lance Corporal]]\n| colspan=2| [[Aircraftman]]\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Military ranks by country}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Military Ranks And Insignia Of Norway}}\n[[Category:Military ranks of Norway]]\n[[Category:Military insignia|Norway]]\n", "text_old": "{{Norwegian defence}}\n'''Military ranks and rank insignia of Norway''' were changed June 1, 2016, with the reintroduction of the [[Non-commissioned officer|Non-Commissioned Officer Corps]], and the abolishment of the one-tier officer system in place since 1975.<ref name=reg_pers>{{Kilde www |url=https://www.regjeringen.no/no/aktuelt/forsvaret-innforer-ny-personellordning/id2416765 |tittel=Forsvaret innf\u00f8rer ny personellordning |bes\u00f8ksdato= 2017-02-01|forfatter= |utgivelsesdato= |dato=2015-06-12 |utgiver=Regjeringen |spr\u00e5k=norsk }}</ref>\n\n==New system of 2016==\nThe [[Storting]] adopted in 2015 the new scheme for military personnel, ''Milit\u00e6rordningen''.<ref name=\"reg_pers\"/> From 2016, the Norwegian Defence Forces have two career ladders for the military personnel; one officer scheme for personnel who with a degree from the military academy, or a university degree and qualification courses, and a non-commissioned officer scheme for personnel with non-commissioned officer school.<ref name=nyegrad>{{Kilde www |url=https://forsvaret.no/aktuelt/ny-militaerordning |tittel=Her er de nye gradene |bes\u00f8ksdato= 2017-02-01|forfatter= |utgivelsesdato=2015-12-11 |dato= |utgiver=Forsvaret |spr\u00e5k=norsk }}</ref><ref name=tj_12_3>{{Kilde www |url=https://forsvaret.no/fakta_/ForsvaretDocuments/TJ%2012-3-2%20Bestemmelse%20for%20H%C3%A6rens%20distinksjoner%20og%20andre%20uniformstegn.pdf |tittel=TJ 12-3-2 Bestemmelse for H\u00e6rens distinksjoner og andre uniformstegn, s. 10|bes\u00f8ksdato= 2017-02-01|forfatter= |utgivelsesdato=2016-04-26 |dato= |utgiver=Forsvaret |spr\u00e5k=norsk }}</ref>\n\n===Commissioned officers===\nThe rank insignia for commissioned officers for the army, navy and air force respectively.\n{| style=\"border:1px solid #8888aa; background-color:#f7f8ff; padding:5px; font-size:95%; margin: 0px 12px 12px 0px;\"\n{{Ranks and Insignia of NATO Armed Forces/OF/Blank}}\n{{Ranks and Insignia of NATO Armies/OF/Norway}}\n{{Ranks and Insignia of NATO Navies/OF/Norway}}\n{{Ranks and Insignia of NATO Air Forces/OF/Norway}}\n{{Ranks and Insignia of NATO Armed Forces/OF/Blank}}\n|}\n\n===Enlisted===\nThe following are the 